shore-party
Homonym Number: 1
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a party engaged in shore whaling; operating from a shore whaling station, not from a mother ship
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:-
Pronunciation:
