Citations
Date: 25/1/1850
Source: Daily Southern Cross
Author:
Vol / Page: 3
Edition:
Quote: In recent numbers we have reported the arrivals of several whalers in the northern ports; who, we are glad to learn, have been very successful in their operations off our coasts. We are also gratified to find that several shore parties on the east coast have been equally fortunate.
